BEAT_SEQUENCE, CASE_BREAKDOWN, CAUSE_CHAIN, CENTER_FOCUS, CHAT_BUBBLE, CHECKLIST_REVEAL, COGNITIVE_SHIFT, CONCEPT_CARD, DATA_TABLE, DOS_AND_DONTS, KPI_HERO, MAGNIFYING_GLASS, METHOD_STACK, PANEL_GRID, PEER_INDUCT, PROGRESS_RING, QUOTE_CITATION, SPLIT_COMPARE, STAT_COMPARE, STEP_LIST, TEXT_FOCUS, TIMELINE

选型规则以主提示词中的决策树与自检清单为准；参数结构不在此展开，后续步骤会按 Schema 生成 `param`。

